Harmony Gold Mining Company has announced its financial and operating results for the interim period ended 31 December 2019. “We remain committed to our safety and health journey we embarked upon in calendar year 2016, with our focus on leadership, risk management and people. Read more about gold "Key related elements of this journey are our four-layered risk management approach and attaining a proactive safety culture. "While a stronger gold price received continues to provide a welcome boost to our financial performance, we will focus our efforts on what we are able to control being safety, costs and production”, says Peter Steenkamp, CEO of Harmony.